Subject: How to download installation MSI
Description:
Good morning team,
I'm working for a French company named Socomec.
We purchased Pingcastle Pro licence through a partner, Athéo Ingénierie, but we don't understand how to download the MSI package.
Can you please tell us how to do ? 
Thank you.
What_We_Know__c: Customer wants to locate installation files for PingCastle
Next_Steps__c: First, i attached the installation file but it doesn't work this way. Advised by Brandon to refer them over to the Netwrix.com/support website and register as SOCOMEC to access those files.
Solution_Comment__c: Customer needed a location to download the PC MSI. Referred them to go to their netwrix.com account and find the products there.
